{"tid":621383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國遊客賓館猝死 揭友人藏百萬可卡因","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae56a666ef56b17ff99ae9c0657a8408054fdae","tid":621383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355502&d=c0cgvjwHXMmVisdxPFAbKJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=92b4f02b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355502&h=5bf61c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355502</a><br />\n<br />\n馬國遊客賓館猝死<br />\n揭友人藏百萬可卡因<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】油麻地彌敦道383號平安大樓一間賓館，昨日下午1時半，一名29歲的馬來西亞籍男住客在房內昏迷，同行23歲友人連忙報警。救護車到場將事主送往廣華醫院搶救，但證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者事前曾向職員表示不適，隨後便暈過去。警方正調查事件，包括了解事主的病歷，並聯絡其親友。消息稱，警方於其中一人的行李內撿獲約1.4公斤可卡因，拘捕死者的23歲友人，涉嫌藏毒。警方正展開調查。"},{"pid":"5e3b6148c83c9fbccb2175dbbacbfe00525c9028","tid":621383,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"死後累街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f8b37e8407427204c29bd388f8fb6d1ea13dea","tid":621383,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"試貨試到 OD"}]}